WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:09.567
Our mission is to transform ordinary homes into wellness homes. Spaces that keep you, your family, and the planet safe.

2
00:00:11.367 --> 00:00:24.067
How it started: Magppie Group has been in business for over 50 years. Magppie launched in 2000, introducing steel — and later stone-based design — to the Indian market.

3
00:00:25.867 --> 00:00:35.367
By 2007 Magppie had expanded internationally across 35+ countries, opening its first international retail store in Sydney.

4
00:00:37.167 --> 00:00:47.567
The pivot: for the past 20+ years the focus has been kitchens and wardrobes — and the first SilverStone kitchen was installed in late 2016.

5
00:00:49.367 --> 00:00:56.533
In 2023 came the Wellness Kitchen category: the world's first 100% stone modular kitchen.

6
00:00:58.333 --> 00:01:10.233
Why stone, not wood? Stone kitchens are termite-safe and fungus-safe, and release no formaldehyde into the home — materials that protect the people who live with them.

7
00:01:12.033 --> 00:01:26.433
How it's going: in February 2026, the 'Most Unexpected' honor at KBIS Innovation Hour in Orlando, alongside Caesarstone and LG — and a store now open in Florida, USA.

8
00:01:28.233 --> 00:01:35.633
Every Wellness Kitchen carries a 25-year unconditional guarantee, with a complimentary service visit every year.

9
00:01:37.433 --> 00:01:42.867
Ordinary homes, into wellness homes. This is Magppie.

